"payment_methods/terminals/worldline>`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices.rst:12
msgid ""
":doc:`Connect an Ingenico payment terminal <../../sales/point_of_sale/"
"payment_methods/terminals/ingenico>`"
